Class JtsLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.colorado.cires.cmg.mvt.adapt.jts.model.JtsLayer

  • public class JtsLayer
extends Object

    JTS model of a Mapbox Vector Tile (MVT) layer.

    A layer contains a subset of all geographic geometries in the tile.
